{
  "stem": "888.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you know, on the march, it was like for a a free-for-all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't-- if you just stepped out or you couldn't get along, they would drag you out and, and just shoot you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway-- Stay with the march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tell me more about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, we were marching, marching towards this particular-- well, we didn't know our destination.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where they are taking us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after a while-- I suppose this particular camp was a larger camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there was the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a big camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there must have been, from other camps, you know, they brought people in, you know, to evacuation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Near, near Hirschberg.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- near Hirschberg, there was a camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they called it a [? kranken's ?] camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for some reason or other, which God only knows, they took so many people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think it was more than about maybe 50 people, for some reason or other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came into this particular camp, Hirschberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In this particular Hirschberg, there was evacuations going on from everywhere, which is, you know, camps from all over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they brought the people in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then from there, they evacuated them again, marching further.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, they, they said-- you know, they called out that anybody who doesn't feel, you know, that he could walk any more should-- you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were resigned, me and my brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because my brother was much weaker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was resigned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't-- I says, whatever happens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't necessarily know if they're going to take us any place, or-- I says, whatever happens happens.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they took us for a small-- oh, I think a few kilometers.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
